"content": "<h2>Large flocks and herds</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:3\">JOB 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:43\">GEN 30:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:38\">EXO 12:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:1\">NUM 32:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:8\">JOS 22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:1-2Sam12:3\">2SA 12:1–12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:32\">JER 49:32</a></p>\n<h2>Large cities</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:1\">DEU 9:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:28\">NUM 13:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:28\">DEU 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:10\">DEU 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:2\">JOS 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:12\">JOS 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:13\">1KI 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:4\">NEH 7:4</a></p>\n<h2>Large armies</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:4\">JOS 11:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:20\">NUM 20:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:17\">2KI 18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:24\">2CH 24:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:15\">EZK 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:11-Dan11:13\">DAN 11:11–11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:25\">DAN 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:2\">JOL 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Large crowds of people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:25\">MAT 4:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:9\">2CH 15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:5\">2CH 30:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:13\">2CH 30:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:1\">EZR 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:1\">MAT 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:29\">MAT 20:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:46\">MRK 10:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:47\">MAT 26:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:1\">MRK 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:34\">MRK 6:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:29\">LUK 5:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:11-Luke7:12\">LUK 7:11–7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:27\">LUK 23:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:9\">JHN 12:9</a></p>",
